    • Constructor Detail

      • ClassnameToClassTransformer

        public ClassnameToClassTransformer()
        Creates a ClassnameToClassTransformer using the current thread context ClassLoader to load the classes from given class names. If a contextClassLoader could not be found, falls back to the class loader of this ClassnameToClassTransformer instance.

      • ClassnameToClassTransformer

        public ClassnameToClassTransformer(ClassLoader classLoader)
        Creates a ClassnameToClassTransformer using the provided ClassLoader to load the classes from given class names. If classloader is null, fallback to default behaviour.
        Parameters:
        classLoader - The ClassLoader which should be used to load the Classes for each given fully qualified class name. If classloader is null, fallback to default behaviour.
        See Also:
        ClassnameToClassTransformer()
